First thing first. Perfect Owlbears.<br>
So i went on a long hike to Hollowshade Moor, where there normally are hundreds of Owlbear. But (censured) Not a single one. Instead there were Grimlings all over the place. What happeden here. The other players in the zone, didn't know either. I went to Shar Vahl, to check the vendors. Mayby i could get really lucky, but no.<br>
