<br>
The best (only?) place to get the perfect pelts is the Owlbear Cave in Hollowshade Moor.<br>
<br>
If you head towards the Grimling Forest from Shar Val, there's a path that turns off just before the first bridge.  Following it will lead to the caves.  The drop rate is fairly low, but it varies -- I killed them for forty-five minutes the other day without a single pelt, and then I got two in about thirty seconds.<br>
